data.description: Move right into this outstanding 2 story, end unit townhome in the Prairie Lake Lodges neighborhood of Lakeville. Over 1800 sq ft of space featuring an ample kitchen with a large pantry and stainless-steel appliances, informal dining, a comfy living room with gas fireplace and an awesome patio on the ground level.  Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, convenient  laundry room plus a huge loft/family room.  The primary bedroom has a walk in closet and its own full en-suite bath including a soaking tub and separate walk in shower.   Easy access to I35 and close to walking/biking trails, restaurants, shopping and all that Lakeville offers.  ISD 194 schools.  This is the 3 bed, 3 bath, 2 car townhome you've been looking for! Book a showing today!
